reviewText: Our congregation had already gone through Idleman's "Not a Fan" study. This is an excellent follow-up or can stand on its own as well.
My entire family really enjoyed this movie.
Very good and very well done
Just awesome! I HIGHLY recommend anything from Kyle Idleman!!! He puts the messages in a simple but straight forward, easy to understand format.

Kyle has a way of making you feel like you are actually there while the events are taking place. He also tells the story from Jesus' mother Mary and I really liked the way it made me think of how she must have felt. It will really grab your heart. You may want to order 2 because you know if you loan out yours you probably won't get it back.
Great video but this is no the small group DVD. It is the full length video. Not what I was expecting.
This movie was not the best, it lacked the essence necessary to capture an audience. Even with this being for a biblical story it doesn't have to be boring.
If you are going to be a Christian this is one of the best series on Easter I have seen.
This was an excellent movie depicting Easter.
